headline: JPMorgan Stock Slides on Warning of Steep 2026 Expense Growth
summary: JPM shares slide after the bank warns that 2026 expenses may surge more than $9B on growth spending, tech investments and inflation pressures.

headline: Citi expects this chipmaker to deliver a ’significant beat and raise’ next week
summary: Investing.com -- Citi analysts highlighted one stock they believe will post results “significantly above Consensus” when it reports fiscal first-quarter earnings on Dec. 17 after the close.

headline: Equities Trading Boom To Fuel 10% Rise In 2025 Investment Bank Revenues
summary: Revenues at the world's largest investment banks are expected to grow about 10% in 2025, led by a surge in equities trading.
